Photo: SuppliedShe said Mario was originally from Mozambique.Gauteng police spokesman Mavela Masondo referred Daily Sun to the Independent Police Investigative Directorate.Ipid spokesman Moses Dlamini said the dead cop was charged with murder. “We are investigating the incident.“Burying the victim is not Ipid’s responsibility. The family can bury the loved one and claim the money from the South African Police Service, because the cop was working for them.”
